<p><em>“Crowdfunding describes the collective cooperation, attention and trust by people who network and pool their money and other resources together to support efforts initiated by other people or organizations.” - Wikipedia</em></p>

<p>smartn.me is the first crowdfunding platform in the U.S. that focuses solely on helping you further your education. Whether you’re seeking a college degree, specialized training, books & fees, or the opportunity to study abroad, consider tapping into the crowd to fund your education instead of debt ridden student loans & credit cards.</p>

<p>Our vision is to transform the way you view an education by exposing the many ways that people are learning all over the world. We also hope to present an alternative way to fund your learning ventures  without having a rain cloud of debt looming over your future. If you have any questions please contact us at <a href=mailto:contact@smartn.me>contact@smartn.me</a>.</p>

